title: PHOTO RECAP: Miss Universe 2016 Preliminary Competition
text:
PHOTO RECAP: Miss Universe 2016 Preliminary Competition See the ladies at the swimsuit and evening gown competitions! Published 8:53  57 PM, January 26, 2017 MAXINE MEDINA. Miss Universe Philippines Maxine Medina introduces herself at the pageant's preliminary competition. Photo by Alecs Ongcal/Rappler 
  Miss Universe 2016 Preliminary Competition was held on Thursday, January   
The event was hosted by Miss Universe 2015 Pia Wurtzbach and actor Derek Ramsay. 
The competition kicked off with each girl proudly announcing her name and country. 
The swimsuit competition followed, with the ladies working the stage in Yamamay swimsuits. 
The evening gown competition came next, with the ladies in elegant dresses. Screengrab   
After the preliminaries, audiences stayed to watch the national costume presentation, which is filmed ahead of coronation night. 
  coronation night will take place on Monday, January 30, at the Mall of Asia Arena. â€“
